<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Financial AI Hub</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            height: 100vh;
            width: 100vw;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6d3cc5, #ff69b4);
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .nav-bar {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 60px;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0 20px;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .nav-bar img {
            height: 40px;
            max-width: 100px;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .other-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        .other-links a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            padding: 8px 15px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .other-links a.about{
            background-color: #ff69b4;
        }

        .other-links a.login {
            background-color: #ff69b4;
        }

        .other-links a.signup {
            background-color: #ff69b4;
        }

        .other-links a:hover {
            background-color: #e42688;
        }

        .hero {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            max-width: 800px;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .cta-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #ff69b4;
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            color: #6d3cc5;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .features {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 200px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 36px;
            color: #6d3cc5;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .feature-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .feature-description {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            color: white;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="nav-bar">
        <div class="nav-links">
            <img src="/static/sankalpa.png" alt="Logo">
        </div>
        <div class="other-links">
            <a href="/about" class="about">About us</a>
            <a href="/login" class="login">Login</a>
            <a href="/register" class="signup">Sign Up</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero">
        <h1>Financial AI Hub</h1>
        <h2>Welcome to the Future of Financial Intelligence.</h2>
        <p>InsureInsights is your next-generation AI-powered platform designed to revolutionize financial services. From personalized policy recommendations to real-time fraud detection, our suite of tools empowers users to make smarter, faster, and more secure financial decisions.</p>
    
        <div class="cta-buttons">
            <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
            <a href="/login" class="btn btn-secondary">Sign In</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        &copy; 2025 Financial AI Hub. All rights reserved.
    </div>
</body>
</html>
